            <title>[SPR-416] Lookup problem in ClassPathXmlApplicationContext</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-416</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>
&lt;p&gt;It seems like the lookup of configuration files via the classpath using ClasspathXmlApplicationContext does not work properly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the forum:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/viewtopic.php?t=1489&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/viewtopic.php?t=1489&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;br/&gt;
Andreas&lt;/p&gt;</description>
